OL,3,CAston Villa through to Europa League
OL,4,Cfinal after win against Nottingham
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,FAston Villa are through to the Europa
OL,8,FLeague final after beating Nottingham
OL,9,FForest 4-0 in the second leg and 4-1
OL,10,Fon aggregate.
OL,12,FUnai Emery's side will play Freiburg
OL,13,Fin the final in Istanbul on May 20.
OL,15,FGoals from Ollie Watkins, Emi Buendia
OL,16,Fand two goals from John McGinn earned
OL,17,FVilla's place in the final
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
