OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778234502
OL,3,CAston Villa through to Europa League
OL,4,Cfinal after win against Nottingham
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,FChris Wood's goal in the first leg at
OL,8,Fthe City Ground meant Nottingham
OL,9,FForest came to Villa Park with a one
OL,10,Fgoal advantage.
OL,12,FBut the tie was level in the first
OL,13,Fhalf when Ollie Watkins gave Aston
OL,14,FVilla the lead on the night in the
OL,15,F36th minute.
OL,17,FAfter half-time Aston Villa were
OL,18,Fawarded a penalty after Nikola
OL,19,FMilenkovic pulled down Pau Torres,
OL,20,Ffollowing a VAR check.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
